    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i get that. but like, if we're talking about the actual urgency of the climate crisis, can we really afford to just rely on renewables? like is nuclear basically a necessity at this point if we actually want to meet those net-zero goals?",
      "source": "evaluator"
