    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "so if most models and experts say it's basically crucial for hitting those targets, doesn't that mean the debate about whether we should use it is kind of over? like, if the science says we need it to avoid disaster, isn't focusing on the downsides just a way of delaying the inevitable?",
